{"tid":507125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中醫藥粉含西藥　病人服後肝衰竭","createTime":"2017-12-23T01:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T09:36:07.000Z","uid":60628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"073b16feb228bbf6dcc2df317790d7a42c658952","tid":507125,"uid":60628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T01:55:33.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171223/20253324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F20253324&d=%2F%2B5%2Bqc2hEJKMc6pdDVG3IzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=a5f90f62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F20253324&h=ea18df28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171223/20253324</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗榮興中西藥行駐診中醫師石昭榮，涉嫌向病人處方含未標示西藥「撲熱息痛」的「㾀風散」藥粉，一名64歲女子服用藥粉後出現急性肝衰竭，需接受深切治療，現情況穩定並轉到普通病房。衞生署昨公佈，與警方採取聯合行動拘捕該名中醫，他涉嫌非法製造及管有未經註冊藥劑製品。上述藥粉驗出微量撲熱息痛，低於一般臨床中毒水平，衞生署正調查事件。"},{"pid":"7996aeefb292e72f3f1b3001eeccfb350c6a4db7","tid":507125,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958a3f3202cdc44db60151806dbbac1d672a414c","tid":507125,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港中毒換肝差唔多有一成都係因為食中藥"},{"pid":"3e4d6a53a4d23e891b64f89da3329c5631c9bca1","tid":507125,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港中毒換肝差唔多有一成都係因為食中藥</blockquote><br />\n經食西藥治療，最後都要換肝既有幾多？"},{"pid":"32cdd50e3ea8c395d66c64d11bdbb2d52a59ada8","tid":507125,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike